data.title: Register a Tournament Â· Disc Golf Scene
data.meta_description: Register your disc golf tournament and handle registration and communication with disc golfers.
data.text:
Enter the club / organization name. A new account for the club will be created automatically.

If you are running this event by yourself, you may enter your name instead of a club or organization.

This must be a verified PayPal account with an associated bank account to withdraw funds.

Entry fees are paid directly from the registrant to this account immediately upon each registration.

Registration will open automatically on this date and time.

We recommend a start date no earlier than 180 days before the registration end date.

Registrations can be easily refunded or canceled up to 180 days after the original transaction.
